[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering JSON dependencies**\n\nI'm thinking about whether there's a need for the extra dependency `com.fasterxml.jackson.core:jackson-databind:2.18.2` for better JSON handling with POJOs. This library is typically paired with an asynchronous HTTP client. Most of the features seem accessible through a local `HttpServer` setup, so I wonder if Docker is even necessary in this situation. There’s a lot to consider when aligning the dependencies with project needs!\n\n**Researching technical issues**\n\nI’m looking into a potential issue where existing setups might not be working correctly. The failure could be due to switching to FFM and having no native access. I should investigate the error stack for insights. It seems like focusing on Netty 4.2.2 and possibly Java 24 could yield some insights. I need to dig deeper to understand how these components interact and clarify the source of the problem.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0c8f081531c55ef9016a4134d426b081908bc6d8311f8f22dc\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqQTTibUCXX3i_7AVIX57g2RWvqdrIpOhhUtNatL3SRAb8iACjprb4L4dkMVEbeAxAJwaroGHsgAtwbay57Xq_GviIVEH6uNuHk-cAb4K-ypdTw2jLIu3LChRn6LtPibNnw2nnwkUIUxQBpV60vAxD13SsNYBsKl9faFBYQo8AW4qzHqTzvIz7pXJMXmJ94fzY0nW87fHPpRDPL-92TmxbPs4OasdtL39Ozgz_VO6WkdDRCfORzia_lCE2apq1rueZKqF979b9ua5cRfGUpiVCe310RHn0OX0Zmyqv_SP7hr7Xbls-K0uXp4aUZ4-tCgVDO6823a-TjX1UkeciQG1ilI7BoOw0YkYnrvCySJKiH9wuiNRuC7__NvM8wciRpQUTRlQ7DCrxjwR4WMkJV8maHXJsJh2cKCv9CL1YeHSRcybrHTiNYRbyMVGCAMtSaNgKPvSliyqVwQwt_udRVK1h5cC9Z9E0VPgFwX460EMA5pM_L2nC-FJkHhwPI4saV5KvjB9W6cb6kpS_8gc_QVGsbFkcOu8rLygcqSTxL_35I5RMRLA5Utfpg-WIT4QXqta8fI3GPfodIZJ3ItQjFUj6tLhGAjbqj-Vj-8oZcmZrV7YO16wrMHfvgXZeek__6GaNg4WNVBVynKEUDkrNtLB-P7FoIIMcQ1jMrILkfu9DJA7zyE5kQkxCdJBxBl4e1w0R4Tia3-Jui6zSW8eO3OdBQ5a_FFM1gybyUYS8JyxGdbZ9eK6QtxlDuRdkGyOvMWu3IzFjNxrq01kiIAzMj6gVOl23TxUBsmQ593CRfVgLYxAb3zDNh